    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>恐龙小当家》</strong>是独立团队开发的融合“沙盒驯龙x肉鸽战斗x双人联机”的轻策略冒险游戏，8月 12 日登陆 Steam。玩家可驯养 40 只特性各异的迪诺兽，建造 42 座功能建筑，征服 60 头远古巨兽，支持双人联机，玩法丰富，可畅玩, 40 小时以上</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>驯龙系统</strong>:迪诺兽能生产能战斗，可通过交配、孵化继承特性，自由组建“防御墙”“人海流”等流派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>肉鸽战斗</strong>:四大生态战场搭配 70 种遗物、39 类图腾，可灵活切换战术，应对不同强敌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沙盒建造</strong>:42 座建筑支撑资源产出与家园经营，玩家可自由选择管理风格，平衡生产力与乐趣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>联机体验</strong>:本地/远程双人联机，协同作战或建造，乐趣加倍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开服福利</strong>:首发 14天9折特惠，DEMO 测试玩家免费领限定「猾裹套」时装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>恐龙小当家》</strong>融合多元玩法，福利丰厚，8月12日 抢先体验版上线! <br>即刻加入官方玩家群(群号:907096102)，组队开荒、流驯龙技巧，共闯史前世界，开启狂欢冒险!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即加入愿望单，抢先征服史前世界!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/e0f869c577a38a22752d889ffb973334.poster.avif?t=1757424655\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/e0f869c577a38a22752d889ffb973334.webm?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/e0f869c577a38a22752d889ffb973334.mp4?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沙盒建造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在家园中搜集各类资源,研究科技,自由建造,提升据点规模.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/ef3494f697d92dbb9cd25be7342d2ea3.poster.avif?t=1757424655\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/ef3494f697d92dbb9cd25be7342d2ea3.webm?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/ef3494f697d92dbb9cd25be7342d2ea3.mp4?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种植生产</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与迪诺兽一同种植,浇水,施肥,收割.与恐龙随从一起建造属于自己的农田</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/6ad0e8cc275644579a5dab857158b1e8.poster.avif?t=1757424655\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/6ad0e8cc275644579a5dab857158b1e8.webm?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/6ad0e8cc275644579a5dab857158b1e8.mp4?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >宠物交配及孵化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迪诺兽可以进行交配,培育出最强基因的工作随从或战斗随从</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/24c46424316cbe9f8f7e68b93dce02aa.poster.avif?t=1757424655\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/24c46424316cbe9f8f7e68b93dce02aa.webm?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/24c46424316cbe9f8f7e68b93dce02aa.mp4?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索秘境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与迪诺兽一同探索秘境,秘境中存在大量稀有随从和材料,同时你需要面临更大的挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/80518fae6aa5956681fb67be873ab586.poster.avif?t=1757424655\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/80518fae6aa5956681fb67be873ab586.webm?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336520/extras/80518fae6aa5956681fb67be873ab586.mp4?t=1757424655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
